The paper deals with social networks and opinion dynamics, which are central topics in the field of social computing (cs.SI) and computational social science (cs.SOC). The optimization problem and algorithm proposed in the paper also involve machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the optimization of objective functions, which is a topic in optimization and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the empirical study involves data analysis and statistical learning (cs.LG).
